2006-08-14  Geoffrey Hutchison  <babel@geoffhutchison.net>

	* src/ASphereRender.h, src/ASphereRender.cpp: Example rendering
	class, generates VdW spheres for a given molecule.

	* src/AGLWidget.h, src/AGLWidget.cpp: Add initial support for
	rotation. Eventually should be moved to a separate class for each
	tool (rotate, orbit, zoom, translate, etc.).

	* src/AMainWindow.cpp: Add minimum size hint (240x320) and # of
	bonds when reading a molecule.

