	* src/main.cpp, src/AMainWindow.h, src/AMainWindow.cpp:
	Switch back to custom main window -- easier to add slots for commands.

	* src/AGLWidget.h, src/AGLWidget.cpp: Add support for rendering GL
	display lists -- renderer classes should generate a display list
	and pass it off to the widget.

